48) Record number handling in PHP with suitable examples
<?php
$students = array("Divya", "Priya", "Karthik", "Meena");
$total = count($students);
echo "Total Records: $total <br><br>";
for ($i = 0; $i < $total; $i++) {
echo "Record " . ($i+1) . ": " . $students[$i] . "<br>";
}
?>
output:
Total Records: 4
Record 1: Divya
Record 2: Priya
Record 3: Karthik
Record 4: Meena
